{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Layouts"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Load cuxfilter and data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from cuxfilter import charts\n",
    "import cuxfilter\n",
    "from bokeh import palettes\n",
    "cux_df = cuxfilter.DataFrame.from_arrow('./data/146M_predictions_v2.arrow')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Declare charts"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#tile provider for choropleth map\n",
    "MAPBOX_API_KEY= \"<mapbox-api-key>\"\n",
    "\n",
    "chart0 = charts.choropleth(x='zip', y='delinquency_12_prediction', color_column='delinquency_12_prediction', color_aggregate_fn='mean',\n",
    "                                  geo_color_palette=palettes.Purples9, mapbox_api_key=MAPBOX_API_KEY,\n",
    "                                  geoJSONSource = 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rapidsai/cuxfilter/GTC-2018-mortgage-visualization/javascript/demos/GTC%20demo/public/data/zip3-ms-rhs-lessprops.json',\n",
    "                                  data_points=1000, nan_color='white')\n",
    "chart1 = charts.bar('dti')\n",
    "chart2 = charts.bar('delinquency_12_prediction',data_points=50)\n",
    "chart3 = charts.line('borrower_credit_score', step_size=1)\n",
    "chart4 = charts.bar('seller_name')\n",
    "chart5 = charts.scatter(x='loan_id',y='current_actual_upb')\n",
    "chart6 = charts.line('dti')\n",
    "chart7 = charts.line('delinquency_12_prediction', data_points=50)\n",
    "chart8 = charts.bar('borrower_credit_score', step_size=1)\n",
    "chart_widget = charts.multi_select('dti')\n",
    "\n",
    "#create a list of charts\n",
    "charts_list = [chart_widget, chart0, chart3, chart1, chart2, chart4, chart5, chart6, chart7, chart8]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Layout Types"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1. Single feature"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<img src= './layout_thumbnails/single_feature.png' style=\"margin-left:35%\" width=350px>"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "d = cux_df.dashboard(charts_list[:2], layout=cuxfilter.layouts.single_feature, theme=cuxfilter.themes.rapids, title=\"Layout - single feature\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 15,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<IPython.core.display.Image object>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "await d.preview()"
   ]
